FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774361471
OL,3,CFisherman takes Lough Neagh fight to
OL,4,Ccourt
OL,6,F"Our father James Gerard Conlon was an
OL,7,Feel fisherman and his father Hughie
OL,8,FConlon before him was an eel
OL,9,Ffisherman," he said.
OL,11,F"Going further back than that, beyond
OL,12,Fmemory, my family would all have been
OL,13,Ffishermen.
OL,15,F"My way of life has been destroyed by
OL,16,Fthe blue-green algae and I want DAERA
OL,17,Fto do whatever is necessary to stop
OL,18,Fthe algae and safeguard and protect
OL,19,FLough Neagh, the fish, the flies and
OL,20,Fthe wildlife for the benefit of future
OL,21,Fgenerations."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]sD@AOUwD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
