FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774361471
OL,3,CFisherman takes Lough Neagh fight to
OL,4,Ccourt
OL,6,FBlue green algae has blighted it for
OL,7,Fmany years due to pollution from
OL,8,Ffarming, wastewater and invasive
OL,9,Fspecies.
OL,11,FThe lough, which is the UK's largest
OL,12,Ffreshwater lake, provides 40% of
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland's drinking water.
OL,15,FA permission hearing is taking place
OL,16,Ftoday at the Royal Courts of Justice
OL,17,Fin Belfast.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
