OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1774361471
OL,3,CFisherman takes Lough Neagh fight to
OL,4,Ccourt
OL,6,FThe proceedings are expected to last
OL,7,Fone day, with a decision expected
OL,8,Fshortly afterwards on whether the case
OL,9,Fwill proceed to the next stage.
OL,11,FUTV has contacted DAERA for a response.
